{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-00135/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-00135"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:01:35"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["high key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man polishes a shoe."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00135/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-00135","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00135/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-00135"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00135/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00135/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00135/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00135/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00135/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00135/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00135/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00135/canvas/1/0bc7633e-ecb4-4e7a-a291-cf05d13abb7c","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T13:46:35.431Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds polishes his shoes with vigor. It’s an act of obsession as much as it is one of cleanliness. This action also serves to establish the initial power dynamic: he appears to be strong and in control. Shoes for the film were made by “bespoke cobbler <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW223040056 BCX0\" href=\"https://www.georgecleverley.com/\"><u>George Cleverley</u></a>, who opened his namesake Mayfair boutique in 1958” (“About the Production,” 21).&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00135/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:602.7352941176468,660.9595588235294,522.5073529411765,206.95588235294122"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00135/canvas/1/e62d255f-8242-46b3-990b-c5a5fd862bcd","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T13:46:52.897Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>This shot frames Reynolds in the middle of the frame, which reinforces his role as protagonist, but he is also in front of a mirror, which symbolizes a split, the tension between a desire for control and, as audiences later learn, a desire to relinquish it. The primarily black and white colors in this shot also underscore this contradiction.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00135/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:498.91544117647055,92.04044117647055,809.8455882352941,491.04044117647044"}}}]}]}]}